mean_en: (of two or more events) to take place at the same time; (of ideas, opinions, etc.) to be the same or very similar; (of objects or places) to meet; to share the same space
sentence: My birthday coincides with my wedding anniversary.
sentence_trans: 我的生日和我的结婚纪念日碰巧是同一天。
word_etyma: co共同 + in进 + cide掉下 → 共同掉进来 → 巧合
